{"tid":1996024,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得宜家啲遊戲太多提示，搞到無咁好玩","createTime":"2020-04-30T16:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T14:40:14.000Z","uid":79075,"like":66,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"ef1e0e3b464e5d857a265f590c70917fcd0b2936","tid":1996024,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"例如Bio re2,3 咁 <br />\n打boss fight 死一次就會係loading screen到講到明個boss弱點係咩，或者點打<br />\n好似直接俾答案咁<br />\n無左搵打法既樂趣<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多遊戲會有好方便既地圖，又會有HUD話你知走邊到<br />\n只要你跟住個icon指既方向無腦走就得<br />\n我一有地圖就會唔覺意依賴地圖走<br />\n周圍有咩風景都好少理，望住個地圖行<br />\n<br />\n雖然係好方便，但好似少左種樂趣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde9d9a1441b9de9ec651a6330a20b4e602010ce","tid":1996024,"uid":49336,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:35:59.000Z","msg":"loading果陣合埋對眼"},{"pid":"aeebe53a355cd29c6719f7f2f1ad938cec07379c","tid":1996024,"uid":82815,"like":13,"dislike":5,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:51:04.000Z","msg":"玩zelda<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6557e66a75ea7aa05058f55a636ba8db35e7ede7","tid":1996024,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:52:22.000Z","msg":"而家啲game太親切，好似內置埋攻略咁。"},{"pid":"9a1ac8ee596dad93e8f636f5d312a5527584793c","tid":1996024,"uid":1977,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:54:21.000Z","msg":"如果死10次先提都唔算過份既"},{"pid":"49cf8bea17c686c5c16699fa8b4711b6eb5921e9","tid":1996024,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeebe53a355cd29c6719f7f2f1ad938cec07379c","tid":1996024,"uid":82815,"like":13,"dislike":5,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:51:04.000Z","msg":"玩zelda<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"有玩啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876a79186afd4d1f6e33a2900e